name: container production, for collection of post-consumer waste plastic for recycling | container, for collection of post-consumer waste plastic for recycling | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/16438/documentation

This dataset was built as a weighted average of regional datasets of the same activityName.  Weights are based on production volumes.;Europe without Switzerland: production volume = 6e+09 unit/year, weight = 0.7627;US: production volume = 2e+09 unit/year, weight = 0.2299;CH: production volume = 6e+07 unit/year, weight = 0.007426

Activity starts with the production of the container for the collection of post-consumer waste plastic packaging material intended for recycling.

This activity ends with the waste material generated by the container at the end of service. Neither losses during production, use and disposal nor infrastructure requirements have been included due to lack of data.

no allocation involved
category: C:Manufacturing/22:Manufacture of rubber and plastics products/222:Manufacture of plastics products/2220:Manufacture of plastics products

processDocumentation.geographyDescription: This dataset is a weighted average built from the following geographies: Europe without Switzerland, US, CH.
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: Uncertainty estimation according to the pedigree matrix
